  <brief_title>CT Guided Injection for Low Back Radiculopathy: A Randomized Clinical Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Trial of CT-guided Perineural Injection With a Corticosteroid Plus a Long Acting Local Anesthetic Versus Standard Medical Management in Patients With Acute Lumbar Radiculopathy and a Corresponding Disc Herniation</official_title>
