  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults &lt;60y

          -  &lt; 1m of symptoms

          -  Symptoms consistent with herniated disc

          -  MRI demonstrates corresponding disc

          -  Back pain resulting in functional disability

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic pain

          -  Daily pain medication

          -  Frequent back pain

          -  On the job injury
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
